THE SA Football Association have appointed yet another foreign coach to guide Bafana Bafana. In Hugo Broos, the country’s football governing body haven't brought in the first “Madala”. The Belgian will be 70 by the time his five-year contract ends. Broos will probably need a walking stick by the time he leads Bafana in the 2026 World Cup... that is if he lasts that long. On this #Throwback Thursday, we look at some of the old-timers and palookas who guided Bafana, including Joel Natalino Santana.        